data.description: **Price Reduction**Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after gated community of Covington Knolls! Nestled on a quiet street with a grand half circle driveway, this stately 2 story home offers privacy, ample space, and recent updates throughout that are sure to satisfy even the most discerning buyers. This spacious floor plan boasts 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, providing plenty of room for a large family or gatherings. The main floor features a stunning executive office, a large open kitchen, as well as, formal living and dining rooms and a family room with fireplace perfect for entertaining. Meticulous attention to detail is evident in the stylish gourmet kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, as well as, stone countertops and backsplash for a sleek and modern finish and walks out to your private deck and tree-lined backyard. Mature landscaping that backs to a beautiful community open space creates a tranquil oasis perfect for relaxing and enjoying Colorado's beautiful weather with a glass of your favorite beverage. The recently updated oversized primary suite features a stunning 5-piece master bathroom with separate his and hers walk-in closets with custom built-in organizers. The second story also offers two other large bedrooms and adjacent remodeled full bathroom. The allure continues in the finished basement, which provides an abundance of additional living space for entertaining. The basement also includes one bedroom, as well as a  3/4 bathroom. The oversized finished 3 car attached garage provides ample workspace. Need more room for the RV? The accommodating RV garage won't disappoint and is heated and has 220 service as well. The neighborhood of Covington Knolls offers an exclusive community experience and has been recognized by homeowners to be one of Greeley's most sought-after communities. Enjoy the breathtaking views and lush landscaping of this gated community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary residence your own!
